title: Which teams got better in Free Agency?
itunes:title: Which teams got better in Free Agency?
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest news around the NFL including Chris Borland's surprising retirement, Philip Rivers' recent comments and more. Plus, which teams got better or worse in free agency?
